<h1>Athletics</h1>

<p>
When I was younger I did not do sports until I was forced to join a club swim team over the summers during middle school. 
I never knew anyone on the team and did not enjoy it too much overall. Then in the spring of 8th grade 
I decided to join the crew team which a bunch of my friends were on and I instantly fell in love with the sport.
</p>



